  "goal": "Nhiệm vụ: Implement a Reactive Stream CQRS Pattern with Event-Driven Pub-Sub to resolve the 'Chain Breaker' mutation error by decoupling the core execution loop from the state mutations, ensuring that every task lane and task state transition is emitted as a clear event rather than a direct method call.\n\n[Dữ liệu Tự Phân Tích]:\n- Ưu điểm mong đợi: Highly resilient against macro-evolutionary dead-ends; eliminates synchronous blocking in the Docker Shadow Workspace; provides full auditability of AgentPhase transitions through an event store; enables asynchronous execution via an'LTC (Long-Term Control) Orchestrator' to prevent loop termination.\n- Rủi ro NGHIÊM CẤM vi phạm: Increased complexity of the core kernel architecture; requires a strict enforcement of the 'Brand' and 'CommandToken' validation within the CoreKernel authority; higher overhead for managing TaskLane and MessageTask streams in a single-threaded environment.",
